---
title: Glazed Cajun Sea Bass with Oven-Baked Spiced Potatoes and Garlic Tenderstem® Broccoli
description: Punchy and smoky with a spicy kick, Cajun spice mix contains ingredients such as chilli powder, ground cumin, oregano and thyme. The Cajun spice and red pepper chilli glaze pairs perfectly with the delicate basa.
